
Running Tests
=============

Create postgres user that is allowed to create db:

sudo -u postgres createuser $USER
sudo -u postgres psql -c "alter user $USER with createdb;"

Dependencies For Compiling C++ Code
===================================

* Boost
* libpq
* JsonCpp
* Python 3

For a complete and up to date list of dependecies and how to install
them on Ubuntu see .travis.yaml

